Description:
You find yourself standing before a massive, withered, ancient yet otherworldly tree. Its bark looks brittle, like one touch might turn it to dust.

Tucked inside its hollow core are flickering candles and fresh offerings of fruit.

And beneath your feet, the soil hums with quiet magic.
